          "timestamp": "19:50"
        },
        {
          "title": "Abaye's Answer: Replanted Grain No Longer Considered Tevel; Cannot Become Terumah While Growing",
          "display_title": "Abaye's Terumah Answer",
          "timestamp": "21:14"
        },
        {
          "title": "Objection: This Would Create Terumah on Growing Grain, Contradicting Established Principle",
          "display_title": "Objection to Terumah",
