        },
        {
          "title": "Parallel from Eggs: Part Inside vs. Outside Bird; Same Principle of Abnormal Consumption",
          "display_title": "Egg in Bird Analogy",
          "timestamp": "25:15"
        },
        {
          "title": "Final Resolution: While Attached, Eating Is Not Considered Normal; Principle Stands",
          "display_title": "Attached Objects Not Eat…",
